VotingStreakNFTModuleTest
├── when voting consecutively
│   └── it should increment streak
├── when missing a cycle
│   └── it should reset streak to zero
├── when reaching ten consecutive votes
│   └── it should mint an NFT
├── when recasting a vote in same cycle
│   └── it should not increment streak
├── when non-owner sets NFT contract
│   └── it should revert
├── when rebuilding a broken streak
│   └── it should track new streak from zero
└── when multiple users vote
    └── it should track independent streaks